snippet.textDisplay: Hats off to the composer and singers.... but my sincere thanks to the sound mixer/engineer of this piece! What balance you guys have achieved between the various components of this composition. Depending on what I want... I can groove to the beat, I can hum the melody, I can shed tears to the lyrics, I can have a cardiac massage from the base guitar, I can get lost and find myself within each musical room of the beautiful mansion you have erected! Good stuff, Madaari Team. Respect.
